data.description: This charming, move-in-ready 1-story home in the community of Falcon Ridge is packed with updates!  This home is sure to please, with a welcoming open floor plan that features a living room, second living space with a cozy fireplace off the kitchen that flows into the dining space, kitchen with breakfast bar and walk-in pantry, inside laundry room, and primary bedroom with full bath.  The backyard provides a covered patio, great for entertaining, and hosts a lawn and privacy fence. The home features many updates, including a new roof, new rear fence, new HVAC, new flooring, and new kitchen cabinets. The home is conveniently located nearby the historical Comanche Lookout Park, shopping and schools, with easy access to 1604 and I-35.   Don't miss the opportunity to make this your next home, book your tour today!
